<document>
    <header>
        <title>ServoMaster: Metadata: <code>servo/silent</code></title>
    </header>
    <body>
        
        <section>
            <title>Definition</title>
            
            <p>
            
                <code>servo/silent</code> <em>feature</em> is true if
                the hardware is able to shut off an individual servo.
                
            </p>
            <p>

                <code>servo/silent</code> <em>property</em> contains
                the currently set shutoff timeout.
                
            </p>
            <p>
                 
                 See <link
                 href="site:meta_controller_silent"><code>controller/silent</code></link>
                 for more information.
                
            </p>
            
        </section>
        
    </body>
